# Plan Slice Checklist

- Confirm SPEC_READY: true is set before starting.
- Evaluate whether plan.md already provides sufficient slice clarity — skip step if yes.
- Slice by bounded context and dependency direction (not by file type or random grouping).
- Each slice must be independently verifiable.
- Assign owner per slice.
- Map dependency edges between slices explicitly.
- Define validation strategy per slice (lowest valid test layer first).
- Update plan.md and tasks.md with refined slice detail.
- Synchronize AGENTS.backlog.md with links to updated plan/tasks sections.
- Commit to existing Draft PR branch (skip if no changes were needed).
